===Pronunciation===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /ʃo/

===Noun===
'''show'''  (''plural:'' [[shows]])
# a broadcast [[program]], e.g. a ''radio show'' or ''television show''
# a [[play]], [[dance]], or other [[entertainment]]
# an [[exhibition]] of items, e.g. an ''art show'' or ''dog show''
# a [[demonstration]], e.g. a ''show of force''

